  Nigerians Left In Awe After Spotting Elephants Roaming Inside A Bush!!! A post shared by  Gossip Mill Nigeria (@gossipmillnaija) on Aug 12, 2019 at 1:55pm PDT  There was pandemonium in Ijebu waterside area of Ogun state as a herd of elephants chased villagers who thronged the forest to catch a glimpse of the animal. A video posted on the Instagram page of “gossipmillnaija” showed the villagers catching a glimpse of the elephants and filming them. Southern, Middle Belt leaders berate PDP BOT chair on RUGA The fun however, turned sour when the elephants in turn started to pursue the youths who were filming their movement. Vanguard